<LP>
   COATS VIYELLA PLC (London) -- This U.K. textiles concern
said it appointed Neville Bain chief executive officer,
effective Oct. 29. Mr. Bain is currently finance director of
Cadbury Schweppes PLC, a British confections and drinks
group. Mr. Bain is succeeding James McAdam, who is leaving
the post of chief operating officer but will remain as deputy
chairman of Coats Viyella.
